# Auction Service - Project Context

This mobile app (Forsa) connects to the **auction-service** backend. All relevant paths, deployment info, and module structure are recorded here.

## Service Location

- **Local Path**: `/home/yousef/Documents/workspace/zonevast/services/auction-service/`
- **Framework**: NestJS (TypeScript)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with TypeORM, schema: `auction`

## Deployment URLs

| Environment | URL |
|---|---|
| **Test (dev)** | `https://test.zonevast.com/forsa` |
| **Local dev** | `http://localhost:3000/api/v1/` |
| **Lambda dev** | `auction-service-dev` on `eu-central-1` |

- **AWS Region**: `eu-central-1` (Frankfurt)
- **S3 Bucket**: `zonevast-zappa-deployments-eu-central-1`
- **API Prefix**: `api/v1`
- **Project ID**: `11`

## Deployment Commands

```bash
cd /home/yousef/Documents/workspace/zonevast/services/auction-service/

# Deploy to dev (test.zonevast.com)
npm run deploy:dev

# Deploy to prod
npm run deploy:prod

# Or manual:
./deployment/build.sh dev && ./deployment/deploy.sh dev
```

## Backend Modules Structure

| Module | Path | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | `src/modules/auth/` | JWT authentication |
| Auction | `src/modules/auction/` | Auction CRUD, listing |
| Bid | `src/modules/bid/` | Bidding system |
| Category | `src/modules/category/` | Auction categories |
| GroupBuying | `src/modules/group-buying/` | Group deals |
| Engagement | `src/modules/engagement/` | Reviews, favorites |
| User | `src/modules/user/` | User profiles, stats |
| Notifications | `src/modules/notifications/` | FCM push notifications |
| WebSocket | `src/modules/websocket/` | Real-time auction gateway |
| Compat | `src/modules/compat/` | Compatibility endpoints |

## Key API Endpoints

All endpoints prefixed with `api/v1`:

- `POST /auth/login` - User login
- `GET /auctions` - List auctions
- `POST /auctions` - Create auction
- `GET /auctions/:id` - Get auction details
- `POST /bids` - Place a bid
- `GET /categories` - List categories
- `GET /group-buying` - Group deals
- `POST /engagement/favorite` - Toggle favorite
- `POST /notifications/register-token` - Register FCM token

## Integration Notes

- JWT auth: token in `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header
- Cross-service calls: Order service via `ORDER_SERVICE_URL`, File attachments via `ATTACHMENT_SERVICE_URL`
- Firebase FCM for push notifications (project: `zonevast-a0ad6`)
- WebSocket for real-time bidding (disabled on Lambda, enabled locally)

